          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CFAttributedStringRef",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " type refers to an object that combines a CFString object with a collection of attributes that specify how the characters in the string should be displayed. CFAttributedString is an opaque type that defines the characteristics and behavior of CFAttributedString objects. ",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Values of type ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CFAttributedStringRef",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " may refer to immutable or mutable strings, as CFMutableAttributedString objects respond to all functions intended for immutable CFAttributedString objects. Functions which accept ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "CFAttributedStringRef",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " values, and which need to hold on to the values immutably, should call ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1542904-cfattributedstringcreatewithsubs",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " (instead of ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1521269-cfretain",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ") to do so.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
